<h1 id="-save-callback-">* .save(<code>callback</code>)</h1>
<h3 id="purpose" permalink="purpose">Purpose</h3>
<p>The <code>save()</code> method updates your record in the database using the current attributes.  It then returns the newly saved object in the callback. </p>
